metadata.name: Misty
metadata.description:
A sudden cold and snow caused a fog at sea surface and ended up this mysterious sea scenery.  
 
Photographer: Alphan YILMAZMADEN  
Taken on January 24, 2010 at Istanbul,Turkey. 
Nikon D300 Camera and Nikkor 105mm DC lens 
4000x2550 px 300 dpi

This is an open edition which will be active for a limited time, minted to;

Connect with more artists, collectors and friends  
Help accelerate during the bear market.
